 from getting involved in criminal acts.(NAN) Vanguard News Nigeria The police command in Zamfara has arrested 18 suspects over the unlawful demonstration, leading to the destruction of property including the Emir of Shinkafi’s palace. This is contained in a statement by the command Public Relations Officer, SP Muhammad Shehu on Sunday in Gusau. ALSO READ: Garba Shehu on 2023: Nigerians… January 3, 2021 In "News" The Police in Zamfara said it averted an attempt by unknown gunmen to attack Wuya Community in Anka Local Government Area of the state, and arrested one suspect. March 3, 2018 In "News" Some irate youths in Zurmi town, Zurmi local government area of Zamfara attacked the community police station demanding that officers should hand over the three suspected bandits arrested by the army to them. July 29, 2018 In "News"